---
title: Tofu and Spinach Tikka with Garlic-Cilantro Rice
description: This Indian-inspired bowl is creamy and fully loaded with flavour from our tikka sauce. The saucy tofu is served over garlic-cilantro rice for a quick weeknight win!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tofu-et-epinards-tikka-31106fe9.jpg
